<plot>Two gangster/soldiers, Remy and Oliver are given orders by their mysterious leader, Commodore Jonathan. The orders are to find the elusive Albatross King. The men search and destroy a bum named Lara's home to no avail. Not long after the older of the two, Remy, disappears - likely kidnapped by the forces of the Albatross King. As Oliver continues the search he slowly becomes more like Remy in appearance and disposition. Oliver is not successful and realizes his search may never end.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?083237</url></doc>
